Detailed Description

Pseudo-random generation of exponentially distributed deviates.

For details about this distribution, see Wikipedia - Exponential distribution.

For details of the algorithm, see Numerical recipes in C (chapter 7)

pdf: f(x) = l*exp(-l*x); l = lambda
